<plot>A young man, Aiden Burroughs, still haunted by the death of his father, moves to New York to pursue a dream of acting. However he soon finds himself cast in a play and a part that he could never have imagined. Aiden, falling for the playwright's daughter, is led through a Coney Island labyrinth of love and madness until past, present, reality and fantasy collide in a shocking revelation leading Aiden back to his childhood home and a past he never wanted. And at the center of it all, the eccentric playwright, Ernest Tanning, and an old secret, waiting to return home.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?592325</url></doc>
